cs2410.assn7.view

Class UserInterface

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.application.Application
      • cs2410.assn7.view.UserInterface

  • public class UserInterface
extends javafx.application.Application
    This class contains a video viewer, which can be used to view several video formats. It features buttons, menu items, event handlers, listeners, etc...
